data.description: Welcome to this handsome brick home nestled in the cul-da-sac within the Longlea neighborhood offering both tranquility and convenience to dining, shopping, and top rated public schools. The foyer opens to the formal dining room, stairs and great room. The kitchen offers a gas cooktop, double ovens, dishwasher, microwave and refrigerator. Additional features include a desk, large walk-in pantry, half bathroom and a spacious laundry room. A spacious great room offers built-in bookcases, fireplace with gas logs and surround sound. The sun room is positioned to overlook the backyard with heated and cooled floor and Pella windows.  The main level offers a primary bedroom suite with a walk-in closet, soaking tub, walk-in shower, heated floors and a private water closet.  This special floor plan offers a primary bedroom suite on the main level and upstairs! Upstairs offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and a game room. The backyard offers a screened in porch, flagstone patio, water feature, irrigation and a drainage system! Two car garage plus a heated and cooled workshop and parking pad.
